nodes.text: Bravo 5 was the personal N-1 starfighter of Dineé Ellberger during the Invasion of Naboo in 32 BBY. The starfighter was equipped with excellent invasion capabilities. Ellberger used the fighter during the Naboo Space Battle.
Bravo 5 appeared in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace but was first identified as such in Star Wars Customizable Card Game.
